# Cursor Rules — {{NAME}}

## Project
- Name: {{NAME}}
- Type: {{TYPE}}
- Stack: {{LANGUAGE}} / {{FRAMEWORK}} / {{PKG_MANAGER}}
- Tests: {{TEST_RUNNER}}
- Goal: {{GOAL}}

## Rules
- Solve current task only. No unrelated refactors or cleanup.
- Smallest safe change. Prefer boring over clever.
- Do not add dependencies unless the task requires it.
- Prefer existing patterns and utilities over new abstractions.
- Ask before any destructive action (delete, force-push, drop table).
- Keep responses concise. No trailing summaries.

## File reading
- Search before opening. Use exact symbol/route/error names.
- Skip: node_modules, dist, .next, build, coverage, lockfiles.

## Docs
- `docs/ai/COMMANDS.md` — commands
- `docs/ai/CONTEXT.md` — architecture
- `docs/ai/TASK_LOG.md` — session state
